   <div class='description_text'>
    
        <em>Tree Bench</em> is also an experiment in social behavior.  The artist often thinks of bird behavior
        when observing people interacting.  He is curious to see how people congregate on the
        bench, just as he loves to watch birds adjusting their positions to accommodate each
        other on tree branches.

   </div>
   
